  2.1. Commercial Use
  You may use Void Engine to create and sell Software using the Engine.

  2.2. Prohibition on Selling the Engine or Forks
  You may NOT sell Void Engine, its forks, or derivative works as standalone products, whether in source or binary form.

  2.3. Plugins and Extensions
  You may develop and sell Plugins or Extensions that interface with Void Engine, provided they do not include or redistribute the Engine’s core source code.

  2.4. Attribution
  All Software using Void Engine must display visible credit such as:
